subject: Tennis
China Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Novak Djokovic won the China Open with a 6-2, 7-6 (4) victory over Marin Cilic of Croatia, and Svetlana Kuznetsova of Russia beat Agnieszka Radwanska of Poland, 6-2, 6-4.
